The paper focuses on the challenges of lifelong learning in the context of sequential supervised learning with emphasis on recurrent neural networks. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper mentions evaluating the models on a benchmark that involves natural language processing tasks, which suggests that it may also belong to the Computation and Language (cs.CL) sub-category. Finally, the paper mentions evaluating the models on image classification tasks, which suggests that it may also belong to the Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV) sub-category.
